                            <comment id="15185576" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Tue, 8 Mar 2016 19:28:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Since there is no direct inheritance relationship between MultiTableInputFormatBase and TableInputFormatBase, a new class is needed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15185628" author="nathan.schile@gmail.com" created="Tue, 8 Mar 2016 19:45:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yuzhihong%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yuzhihong@gmail.com&quot;&gt;Ted Yu&lt;/a&gt; Sorry, I forgot to mention that I would change TableInputFormatBase#calculateRebalancedSplits to be static.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15185664" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Tue, 8 Mar 2016 20:01:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Then first option is viable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
